<refsect1 id="FpContext.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>The <link linkend="FpContext"><type>FpContext</type></link> allows you to discover fingerprint scanning hardware. This
is the starting point when integrating libfprint into your software.</para>
<para>The <link linkend="device-added">device-added</link> and device-removed signals allow you to handle devices
that may be hotplugged at runtime.</para>

</refsect1>
