<refsect2 id="fp-context-enumerate" role="function">
<title>fp_context_enumerate&#160;()</title>
<indexterm zone="fp-context-enumerate"><primary>fp_context_enumerate</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="void"><returnvalue>void</returnvalue></link>
fp_context_enumerate (<parameter><link linkend="FpContext"><type>FpContext</type></link> *context</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Enumerate all devices. You should call this function exactly once
